      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Fuuton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 15 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 3 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 14</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This supremely perverted technique has been forbidden by many a women's rights organisation. You focus Chakra around the target, causing a sharp wind to shred all of their non-mastercraft clothing, completely destroying them. Functional equipment like shuriken holsters is unaffected.</p>\n\n\n\n",
